        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【#肠道不好真的会影响大脑#[并不简单]】专家提示，肠道和大脑有相同的一些结构，也有自己的肠道神经系统，而且具有很多的神经元，会产生很多的激素，甚至会产生...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%82%A0%E9%81%93%E4%B8%8D%E5%A5%BD%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%9A%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%A4%A7%E8%84%91%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%82%A0%E9%81%93%E4%B8%8D%E5%A5%BD%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%9A%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E5%A4%A7%E8%84%91%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#肠道不好真的会影响大脑#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[并不简单]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】专家提示，肠道和大脑有相同的一些结构，也有自己的肠道神经系统，而且具有很多的神经元，会产生很多的激素，甚至会产生与大脑好多种相同的神经递质，所以如果肠道受到了影响，也会影响到大脑的状态。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%82%A0%E9%81%93%E4%B8%8D%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E4%BC%9A%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%82%A0%E9%81%93%E4%B8%8D%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E4%BC%9A%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E5%93%AA%E4%BA%9B%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#肠道不健康会引发哪些疾病#</span></a>？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>专家提醒，很多疾病都跟肠道健康息息相关，比如炎症性肠病、过敏性的疾病等<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%82%A0%E7%99%8C%E6%9D%A5%E4%B8%B4%E6%97%B6%E4%B8%8A%E5%8E%95%E6%89%80%E4%BC%9A%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B04%E4%B8%AA%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%82%A0%E7%99%8C%E6%9D%A5%E4%B8%B4%E6%97%B6%E4%B8%8A%E5%8E%95%E6%89%80%E4%BC%9A%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B04%E4%B8%AA%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#肠癌来临时上厕所会出现4个异常#</span></a> （央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6YY0W1I" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
